description: Aspose.Diagram is a class library for working with Microsoft Visio files. It allows developers to create new diagrams and work with VSD, VSDX, VSTX, VSSX, VSS, VST, VSX, VTX, VDW and VDX files on ASP.NET web applications, web services and Windows applications. It allows you to open files and manipulate the elements of the diagram, from lines and fills, to more complex elements, and then export to VDX, VSX,VSDX,VSSX,VSTX, VTX, XPS, HTML, SVG, SWF, XAML, image or PDF formats.
releaseNotes:
This release introduces the features, enhancements,task and bug fixes as detailed below:
   
   Enhancements  
   DIAGRAMNET-51264-The shadow of shapes is black on converting a VSDM to SVG
   DIAGRAMNET-51270-Cannot see a shape of the VSDX in Visio Viewer
   DIAGRAMNET-51273-Incorrect display of shape in the Visio Viewer 2013
     
    Bugs  

   DIAGRAMNET-51249-Incorrect appearance of the curved line connector in VSDM
   DIAGRAMNET-51250-An additional left parenthesis is added in text on converting a VSD to PDF
   DIAGRAMNET-51251-The size of icon is downgraded on converting a VSDM to SVG   
   DIAGRAMNET-51253-Incorrect color of text and borders in shapes when converting a VSDM to SVG   
   DIAGRAMNET-51255-An image at the bottom has been squashed on converting a VSDM to SVG
   DIAGRAMNET-51258-Open and save routine of VSDM - the length of the walls is changed
   DIAGRAMNET-51259-Open and save routine of VSDM - the length of the walls is changed
   DIAGRAMNET-51260-Index out range error occurred on calling the layout method of Diagram class
   DIAGRAMNET-51263-An additional red color tag appears on converting a VSDM to SVG
   DIAGRAMNET-51265-The font of title text is changed on converting a VSDM to SVG
   DIAGRAMNET-51266-The size of background image is reduced on converting a VSDM to SVG
   DIAGRAMNET-51267-An icon size is downgraded on converting a VSDM to SVG
   DIAGRAMNET-51268-Retrieves incorrect transparency value of an image from VSDM drawing
   DIAGRAMNET-51269-Add virtualization protection
summary: Aspose.Diagram is a class library for working with Microsoft Visio files.
title: Aspose.Diagram for .NET
